{"word":"G2833 - κνήθω - knḗthō - knay'-tho - Itching","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κνήθω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">knḗthō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">knay'-tho</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Itching</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - செவித்தினவாகு"},{"paragraph":"to scratch, tickle, make to itch"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a primary word <b>&#x03BA;&#x03BD;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> <b>knao&#x0304;</b> (to <i>scrape</i>); to <i>scratch</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>tickle:</i> - X itching.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}